title: Leading a Dog’s Life Isn’t Always So Bad
text:
It isn’t easy being top dog.
Being combed and blow-dried. Getting treats—and kisses. Posing for a selfie with a woman wearing heart-shaped glasses. Oh well, it was Valentine’s Day, after all.
